Nowotny Says European Banks Can Get ‘Vast Amounts’ of ECB Loans

-- B y   B o r i s   G r o e n d a h l
-- 
2011-09-20T15:03:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-20/nowotny-says-european-banks-can-get-vast-amounts-of-ecb-loans.html
European Central Bank Governing
Council member Ewald Nowotny said European banks have enough
collateral to get “vast amounts” of ECB loans, according to an
interview with the Wall Street Journal.  Nowotny “hit back” at what he called “waves of
hysteria” over the condition of European banks, the newspaper
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Boris Groendahl in Vienna at 
